  "title": "Admin Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>· Provide administrative support for all Examinations</p><p>· Assist in the preparation and documentation on Examination related Matters</p><p>· Assist in verification of Students’ Data & updating Teachers’ Data</p><p>· Assist in briefing exercise to all Examination personnel</p><p>· Assist in the printing of Examination Papers</p><p>· Assist in all the administrative related work to Centralized Examinations and Centralized Marking Exercise</p><p>· Assist in the preparation of Appointment letters for Invigilators, Markers and In-charge of Viewing exercise for all the Examinations</p><p>· Assist in preparing consolidated list of Board Classes by the Examination rooms for batching of ruled papers, OAS.</p><p>· Assist in printing students’ attendance and mark sheets</p><p>· Assist in the marking of OAS using OMR.</p><p>· Assist in printing performance reports by examination rooms</p><p>· Assist in the uploading of marks to MOE</p><p>· Assist in ad-hoc assignments when required</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><p>· GCE or Diploma with at least 2 years of working experiences</p><p>· Proficient in all Microsoft Office Applications is preferred</p><p>· Independent, committed, hardworking and analytical</p><p>· Meticulous with attention to details</p><p>· Able to multi-task and work under tight deadlines</p><p>· Candidate must be a Singaporean or Singapore PR</p><p>· Good communication skills</p><p>· Able to start work immediately or within short notice</p>",
